' -----------------------------------------------

'' This property gets or sets the touring machine to calculate the bounding box top left point x-coordinate.
Property X As TouringMachine

'' This property gets or sets the touring machine to calculate the bounding box top left point y-coordinate.
Property Y As TouringMachine

'' This property gets or sets the touring machine to calculate the bounding box width.
Property Width As TouringMachine

'' This property gets or sets the touring machine to calculate the bounding box height.
Property Height As TouringMachine

'' This property gets or sets the touring machine to calculate the corner radius in x-direction.
Property RX As TouringMachine

'' This property gets or sets the touring machine to calculate the corner radius in y-direction.
Property RY As TouringMachine


