'' Constructs a new styleable (rounded) rectangle. Base class **Styleable** is.
''
'' The **xValue** defines the bounding box top left point x-coordinate.
'' The **yValue** defines the bounding box top left point y-coordinate.
'' The **widthValue** defines the bounding width.
'' The **heightValue** defines the bounding height.
'' The **rxValue** defines the corner radius in x-direction.
'' The **ryValue** defines the corner radius in y-direction.
Public Sub _new(xValue As TouringMachine, yValue As TouringMachine, widthValue As TouringMachine, heightValue As TouringMachine, rxValue As TouringMachine, ryValue As TouringMachine)
  $fX = xValue
  $fy = yValue
  $fWidth = widthValue
  $fHeight = heightValue
  $fRX = rxValue
  $fRY = ryValue
End

